{"tid":537765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10元便當嬤雲林版！月虧十萬「我心甘情願」","createTime":"2018-01-23T04:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T04:10:54.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e09b149e8b4f98eeba3b25973aa42c1da2efd17","tid":537765,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"據《三立新聞》報導雲林有一家「婆婆的店」，位在虎尾科大側門。高齡85歲的婆婆的店，價格便宜到讓人不可思議，包括湯麵、米粉湯、粿仔條、乾麵、冬粉、滷肉飯，一碗通通只要20元。湯類如丸子湯、餛飩湯、豬腸湯則通通只要10元。不過因為這是婆婆的一人小店，所以人手不足，用完店客人還必須自己洗碗，但大家都相當配合。<br />\n除此之外，婆婆也會準備一些分裝好的米，給家裡有困難的人領取。一個月開店下來，婆婆就要虧損十萬，但她還是笑容滿面地說：「不要講錢，要做就是心甘情願，我開店本來就不是為了賺錢，只要大家都能來看我，我就很開心了！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180123/1283946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180123%2F1283946&d=dKoicb9uGzfvckZArvOw0RxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=e08b7ef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180123%2F1283946&h=546e229f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180123/1283946</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180123/640_5967596cd97e8e1a34bac2d0fb74cbac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180123%2F640_5967596cd97e8e1a34bac2d0fb74cbac.jpg&h=a9fc4286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係香港，一定俾鄰近同行屌死"}]}